<F P=100> REGIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> East Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   Fujian Protects Enterprise Finances From Official Organs </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Fujian Protects Enterprise Finances From Official Organs </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   HK1606132994 Fuzhou Fujian People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 14 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK1606132994 </F>
<F P=104>  Fuzhou Fujian People's Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Mandarin </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] On 8 June, the office of the provincial party 
committee and the office of the provincial government issued a 
notice on halting the abuse of power by party and government 
organs and their working personnel in making use of enterprises' 
finance without compensation. 
  It has been decided that from June to October this year, the 
problem of party and government organs at all levels throughout 
the province and their working personnel making use of 
enterprises' finance without compensation will be dealt with 
seriously in four stages. Marked phased results must be 
achieved to resolutely curb such unhealthy trends. 

</TEXT>

