Delegation" published in the 16 May China on page 6 and was 
found to contain the following variations: 
  Page 6, column one, paragraph eight, only sentence reads: 
...relations with Russia which have not come easily, and wishes 
to... (supplying additional passage). 
  Column one, paragraph ten, only sentence reads: ...positive 
role in further developing bilateral good-neighborliness... 
(adding "further") 
  Column one, paragraph eleven, only sentence reads: 
...happiness with the development of relations between China 
and Russia over recent years and said that both China and 
Russia, sharing a boundary line of over 4,000 km and a heavy 
task of economic development, need a peaceful and secure 
external environment for... (rewording, supplying additional 
passage) 
  Column two, first full paragraph, only sentence reads: ...He 
said that developing sustained and stable... (adding 
"developing") 
  Column two, paragraph two, only sentence reads: ...to 
fulfill the needs and wishes of the... (adding words) 
  Column two, paragraph four, only sentence reads: ...National 
People's Congress. 
  National People's Congress Standing Committee Vice Chairman 
Wang Hanbin, Russian Ambassador to China Rogachev, and others 
took part in the meeting. 
  At noon, Chinese... (supplying additional paragraph) 
  Column two, paragraph five, only sentence reads: 
...Vice-Premier Li Lanqing met with the delegation at the 
Ziguangge Pavilion in Zhongnanhai. 
  The delegation, which... (dropping "also," adding the venue 
of the meeting) 

</TEXT>

