<F P=100> INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> General </F>
<H3> <TI>   Yeltsin Cancels Meeting With SRV Premier </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yeltsin Cancels Meeting With SRV Premier </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW1706104494 Beijing XINHUA in English 1034 GMT 17 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW1706104494 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Moscow, June 17 (XINHUA) -- The meeting of Russian 
President Boris Yeltsin with visiting Vietnamese Prime Minister 
Vo Van Kiet, scheduled for Friday [17 June], has been cancelled, 
the presidential press service announced today without giving 
any explanations. 

</TEXT>

